text: The Assam tree frog, Indian hylid frog, Indian leaf frog, West China tree toad, Gongshan tree toad, Jingdong tree toad, Chuanxi tree toad, Wuling tree toad, Tengchong tree toad, green leave frog, southwestern China tree frog, Jerdon's tree frog, green tree frog, European green tree frog or common tree frog (Hyla annectans) is a tree frog from southern Asia. People have seen it in India, Myanmar, Vietnam, China and Thailand. ==References== Category:Frogs of Asia
title: Assam tree frog
